data.description: This VACANT two-family home located in the desirable Ampere section of East Orange, NJ features exclusive parking, separate utilities, and a partially finished basement. This property offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. With a total of 8 bedrooms, including 5 bedrooms on the second floor featuring a two-level layout in this unit and an additional 3 bedrooms on the first floor with a single-level design, you'll find the ideal living space to suit your needs. Commuting to NYC is also a breeze! Your dream home with ample space and versatile living awaits.
